<h1>振込CSV（住信SBI）</h1>

<div class="alert alert-secondary" role="alert">
  confirmed の精算から振込CSVを生成します（1ファイル最大 9,999 件。超えたら分割）。
  生成したCSVはActiveStorageに保存され、ここからダウンロードできます。
</div>

<div class="mb-3 d-flex gap-2">
  <%= link_to "精算一覧へ", system_admin_settlements_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
</div>

<% if @exports.blank? %>
  <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
    表示できる振込CSVはありません。
  </div>
<% else %>
  <div class="referral-codes-list">
    <% @exports.each do |e| %>
      <div class="card referral-code-card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="referral-code-row">
            <div class="referral-code-label">ID</div>
            <div class="referral-code-value fw-semibold"><%= e.id %></div>
          </div>

          <div class="referral-code-row">
            <div class="referral-code-label">Format</div>
            <div class="referral-code-value"><%= e.format %></div>
          </div>

          <div class="referral-code-row">
            <div class="referral-code-label">Seq</div>
            <div class="referral-code-value"><%= e.file_seq %></div>
          </div>

          <div class="referral-code-row">
            <div class="referral-code-label">Records</div>
            <div class="referral-code-value"><%= e.record_count %></div>
          </div>

          <div class="referral-code-row">
            <div class="referral-code-label">Total</div>
            <div class="referral-code-value fw-semibold"><%= e.total_amount_yen %></div>
          </div>

          <div class="referral-code-row">
            <div class="referral-code-label">Generated</div>
            <div class="referral-code-value text-muted small"><%= l(e.created_at) %></div>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-3">
            <div class="referral-code-inline-actions justify-content-end">
              <%= link_to "詳細", system_admin_settlement_export_path(e), class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
<% end %>
